These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, reading, chess, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, cycling, handball, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
2. the person who's hobby is reading is not the person who's sport is baseball##6
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person who's sport is baseball is not the person who's hobby is chess##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | reading   | skydiving    | cooking    | chess |
| Sport      | volleyball | baseball | handball | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, bus, airplane, scooter
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, grapefruit, lettuce, onion
1. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5
3. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
4. the person driving the bus is not the person eating grapefruit##6
5. the person eating onion is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
6. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
7. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
8. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | bus  | airplane    | boat | scooter    |
| Food       | onion | grapefruit | lettuce  | artichoke |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, sprite, water
4 different pets are kept: turtle, goldfish, frog, rabbit
1. the person drinking water is not the owner of the turtle##6
2. the owner of the goldfish is not the person drinking sprite##6
3. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
4. the owner of the goldfish is the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
6. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the turtle is on the far left or far right##3
8. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | water       | hot-chocolate  | fanta  | sprite |
| Job        | frog | rabbit | goldfish | turtle  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, guinea-pig, hedgehog, snake
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, tea
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
3. the person drinking tea is not the owner of the guinea-pig##6
4. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | hedgehog | snake     | goldfish |
| Transport   | hot-chocolate     | iced-tea    | almond-milk | tea    |

