.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, horror, sports, crime
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, car, snowmobile
1. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the person driving the car##5
3. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
4. the person watching horror movies is not the person driving the snowmobile##6
5. the person driving the bike is not the person watching family movies##6
6. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
7. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | family        | crime | sports | horror |
| Transport   | snowmobile | bike | boat     | car   |

