.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, funk, gospel, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, colombian, indian, polish
1. the australian is on the right of the fan salsa##1
2. the fan soul is not the colombian##6
3. the australian is on the far right##1
4. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
5. the fan gospel is the fan gospel##1
6. the fan gospel is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
7. the fan gospel is somewhere to the left of the fan salsa##5
8. the fan funk is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
9. the fan funk is somewhere to the left of the polish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | funk | gospel    | salsa  | soul   |
| Nationality   | indian  | polish | colombian | australian |

