.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, grey, red, yellow
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, d&b, gospel, reggae
1. the fan gospel is on the left or right of the fan country##3
2. the fan gospel is not the person who likes grey##6
3. the person who likes turquise is the fan d&b##1
4. the fan country is on the left or right of the fan reggae##3
5. the fan gospel is on the far left##1
6. the person who likes grey is the fan country##1
7. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the left of the fan country##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | yellow | grey     | red | turquise |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | country | reggae      | d&b         |

