.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different games are played: billiard, snooker, mah-jongg, whist
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, surfing, swimming, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is golf is not the person playing billiard##6
2. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is not the person who's sport is weightlifting##6
6. the person who's sport is surfing is not the person playing snooker##6
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
8. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | mah-jongg | billiard        | whist  | snooker     |
| Sport   | golf     | weightlifting | surfing | swimming |

