.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, martial-arts, action, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, indie, pop
1. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
2. the fan electronic is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5
3. the fan indie is not the person watching action movies##6
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the fan pop and the person watching action movies##2
5. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
6. the fan electronic is between the fan disco and the person watching horror movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | action | martial-arts    | horror | western |
| Music-Genre   | disco         | electronic | pop   | indie     |

