.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, police-officer, architect, nurse
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, romance, time-travel, western
1. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the right of the police-officer##5
2. the police-officer is not the person watching romance movies##6
3. the entrepreneur is the person watching western movies##1
4. the architect is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
5. the entrepreneur is between the police-officer and the person watching adventure movies##2
6. the police-officer is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | nurse | police-officer      | entrepreneur | architect   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | time-travel | western   | adventure |

