.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-18::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, march, november, december
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, sailing, skateboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's birthday is in march is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6
2. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##5
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2      |       3       |       4       |
| Hobby   | december  | march | september         | november |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | volleyball  | skateboarding | sailing       |

