.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, singing, skydiving, woodworking
City: berlin, hamburg, rome, nizza
1. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to rome##5
2. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##5
3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
4. the person traveling to nizza is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is singing##2
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
8. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | singing | skydiving | board-games | woodworking |
| Pet     | rome  | hamburg      | berlin  | nizza       |

